description:
'Clearlake Comix'

Polaris Adventures, 1981

Written and Illustrated by Bill Leach

For those who don't know, Clearlake is a small town (and a big lake) in Northern California. This comic is kind of cool. It's filled with underground comics style advertisements for Clearlake and the surrounding area, but they're legit. Some of them are probably still there today. It's also pro-environment and tells the story of a 'monster' that lives in Clearlake. 
